{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a6849798ac","title":"火中孤雁","origin":"《四川省右派言论选辑9》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年8月26日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"17580d7542","index":0,"year":1957,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"a6849798ac"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"39ce2a4a60","name":"流沙河"},{"id":"a185c9b36c","name":"四川"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c233a7c22f","type":"title","text":"火中孤雁","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"da30d6bf4a","type":"authors","text":"四川流沙河","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"dc93ad10bd","type":"subtitle","text":"（流沙河：四川成都诗人）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"0674d51ba2","type":"paragraph","text":"春天。一群大雁向北方飞去。    遭到炮火猛击。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"210c51a81a","type":"paragraph","text":"雁群飞到美国，    　　　　　　有一只失群的孤雁，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"0c67dbe8d6","type":"paragraph","text":"被当作了敌机，    　　　　　　漫天回旋，漫天哀啼……","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"d489cb4c60","type":"paragraph","text":"(亲爱的读者，这绝非幻想的童话。请去看1957年2月26日人民日报的消息！)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"cd4fcd5d08","type":"paragraph","text":"侣伴们，侣伴们，你们飞向哪儿去了？    那是什么？那是什么？那是什么？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"40e93bfee0","type":"paragraph","text":"层层的云，茫茫的雾，我到哪儿去找？　　黑压压—大片，拼命怪声地吼叫。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"fc54be426f","type":"paragraph","text":"侣伴们，侣伴们，有什么事情发生了？    一只，两只，三只……排成队伍。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"b811508682","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么突然响起炸雷，天满黑烟缭绕？    从哪儿飞来了这一群凶猛的铁鸟？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"57a7907ae5","type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天亮如镜，白云四面飘，    　　　　　啊，你们，你们，你们要干什么？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"cd7f973e91","type":"paragraph","text":"难道会是一场暴风雨来了？    　　　　　为什么喷着黑烟，把白云染污了？","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"0134520f28","type":"paragraph","text":"我的侣伴们，我的侣伴们，              啊，你们，你们，你们要干什么？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"ec27018d21","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么你们竟把我抛弃了？              为什么吐出火蛇，咬伤我的羽毛？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"c6da68f916","type":"paragraph","text":"请告诉我吧，欢午的纸鹞，              我是什么？一只爱水草爱江湖的雁儿。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"f910df8448","type":"paragraph","text":"这到底是什么事情发生了？              无冤无仇，你们却狠毒地要把我杀掉！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"ff3ac347b8","type":"paragraph","text":"请告诉我吧，微笑的太阳，              我美丽的衣裳和矫健的翅膀燃起来了。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"83ba1a6847","type":"paragraph","text":"这到底是什么事情发生了？              啊，你们这般腰上涂着白星的铁鸟！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"567a622d70","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么，为什么你们不说话呀？          你们是谁？一群披人皮学鸟叫的强盗！","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"16808ae1d8","type":"paragraph","text":"你依旧在欢午，你仍然在微笑。          我想起了，六年前在一个遥远的半岛，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"224ee9ea17","type":"paragraph","text":"侣伴们，你们都躲到哪儿去了？          正是你们，炸毁着每株树和每个雀巢，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"4069d10938","type":"paragraph","text":"出了什么事情，我一点不知道。          喝孤儿的血寡妇的泪，把村庄烧了……","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"2573415117","type":"paragraph","text":"我的侣伴们，你们飞向哪儿去了？　　　  我的情侣，永别了，永别了，永别了！","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"e158be48e7","type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩的天空，我怎能把你们寻到？　　　  我死以后，你不必飞回这儿把我寻找。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"a1820b70a9","type":"paragraph","text":"不要等我了，如果听风我的哀啼，　　　  向前去吧，北方有碧绿而清凉的湖泊。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"563199db57","type":"paragraph","text":"千万莫回头。快些，向北方飞跑！　　　  忘掉我吧，但要牢记那有白星的铁鸟！","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"f5a91fed09","type":"paragraph","text":"而且，当金色的秋天来了，　　　　　　  漫天的回旋，漫天的乱飘，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"1aa5927e8b","type":"paragraph","text":"你们南飞，一定记住绕道：　　　　　　  遍身着了火，生命快完了。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"f61489ff95","type":"paragraph","text":"有星条旗的地方就有死亡，　　　　　　  我用哀啼向大帝呼吁和平，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"ae2f8f87e0","type":"paragraph","text":"宁肯飘洋过海，冒着风暴！　　　　　　  我用死亡向人类控诉强盗！","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"},{"id":"d7333d2772","type":"paragraph","text":" (1957年2月28日雨夜)","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac"}],"page":{"id":"af35c1ec6b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a6849798ac","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}